## 🌐 Traffic Flow (Big Picture)

User  
→ DNS  
→ Cloud Load Balancer  
→ Worker Node  
→ kube-proxy  
→ Ingress Controller Service  
→ Ingress Controller Pod (Nginx)  
→ Ingress Rules  
→ App Service  
→ App Pod  
→ Database Service  
→ Database Pod  

---

## ☁️ Cloud Load Balancer

- Entry point from internet
- Distributes traffic across nodes
- Provides high availability
- Avoids dependency on one node

💡 Created when using:
```yaml
type: LoadBalancer


